#: firefox/new.lang:5
msgid "Firefox for desktop"
msgstr "Firefox ar gyfer y bwrdd gwaith"

#: firefox/new.lang:10
msgid "Different by design"
msgstr "Yn fwriadol wahanol"

#: firefox/new.lang:14
msgid "Proudly<br />non-profit"
msgstr "Yn falch o fod yn<br />ddim er elw"

#: firefox/new.lang:18
msgid "Innovating<br />for you"
msgstr "Arloesi<br />er eich mwyn"

#: firefox/new.lang:22
msgid "Fast, flexible,<br />secure"
msgstr "Cyflym, hyblyg,<br />diogel"

#: firefox/new.lang:26
msgid ""
"As a non-profit, we’re free to innovate on your behalf without any pressure "
"to compromise. You’re going to love the difference."
msgstr ""
"Fel corff ddim er elw, rydym yn rhydd i arloesi ar eich rhan heb orfod "
"cyfaddawdu. Byddwch wrth eich bodd gyda'r gwahaniaeth."

#: firefox/new.lang:30
msgid "Firefox screenshot"
msgstr "Llun sgrin Firefox"

#: firefox/new.lang:34
msgid "Thanks for downloading Firefox!"
msgstr "Diolch am ddewis Firefox!"

#: firefox/new.lang:38
msgid "Start the process by clicking Run."
msgstr "Cychwynnwch y broses drwy glicio Rhedeg."

#: firefox/new.lang:42
msgid ""
"Your download should begin automatically. If not, <a id=\"%s\" href="
"\"\">click here</a>. It could take a few minutes, but it’s worth the wait."
msgstr ""
"Dylai eich llwytho i lawr gychwyn yn syth. Os nad, <a id=\"%s\" href="
"\"\">cliciwch yma</a>. Dylai gymryd ychydig funudau, ond mae'n werth disgwyl."

#: firefox/new.lang:46
msgid ""
"When prompted, drag the Firefox icon into the image of your Applications "
"folder."
msgstr ""
"Pan gewch chi eich annog, llusgwch eicon Firefox i ddelwedd eich ffolder "
"Rhaglenni."

#: firefox/new.lang:50
msgid ""
"Click Run to launch the Mozilla Firefox setup wizard. Then, just follow the "
"steps (we've made the process as painless as possible)."
msgstr ""
"Cliciwch Rhedeg i gychwyn dewin gosod Mozilla Firefox. Yna dilynwch y camau "
"(mae'r broses yn un hawdd iawn)."

#: firefox/new.lang:54
msgid ""
"Drag the Firefox icon from the Applications folder into the dock. Then, just "
"click on Firefox whenever you want to use the web!"
msgstr ""
"Llusgwch eicon Firefox o'r ffolder Rhaglenni i'r doc. Yna cliciwch ar "
"Firefox pryd bynnag rydych eisiau defnyddio'r we!"

#: firefox/new.lang:58
msgid ""
"Now you’re ready to leap boldly into a new era of Web surfing. Double-click "
"on the Firefox icon whenever you want to go online."
msgstr ""
"Nawr rydych yn barod i fentro'n hyderus i gyfnod newydd o syrffio'r we. "
"Rhowch glic dwbl i eicon Firefox pryd bynnag fyddwch eisiau mynd ar-lein."

